column5: Sorry to say but do to the Out of the Storm Music Fest in Goderich on Oct 8th http://outofthestorm.net/tag/goderich/ & one in Exeter to raise money for Tornado Relief on the same date, I don't see how we can hold Music Fest 2011 & do justice to our Sponsors & there for have put it off to a later date Thanx & Tight Lines Richard
